reviewText: The image for the cover is now for Maou no Shiro, but is instead for Yuusha Yoshihiko to Akuryou no Kagi (Hero Yoshihiko and the Demon King's Castle).
Whoever did the subtitles was one lazy mofo. It's nice that it's out with english subs. But couldn't they of found a copy of the show without the news alert in the middle of it?

The DVD screen contained flashing "Earthquake warning".
I believed this DVD set is genuine when I bought it, but I am not sure now.
